`★ Insight ─────────────────────────────────────`
`FarmerState` was a split component holding stamina data that logically belongs on the player. The migration pattern here merges it into `PlayerComponent`, then the `farmerQuery` (which finds entities with `farmerState`) simply becomes `playerQuery` — since stamina now lives on the player entity itself. This is a clean data-locality improvement: one entity, one component, all player state together.
`─────────────────────────────────────────────────`
